20and%20Ukrainian%20representatives%20in%20Riyadh%20for%20the%20first%20such%20parallel%20negotiations%20since%20the%20early%20weeks%20of%20Moscow's%20invasion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20negotiations%20were%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20simultaneously%20to%20enable%20shuttle%20diplomacy%2C%20but%20with%20both%20warring%20sides%20proposing%20different%20plans%20for%20a%20temporary%20truce%2C%20attacks%20have%20continued%20unabated.%20America%20is%20hoping%20that%20going%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20the%20delegations%20can%20pave%20the%20way%20to%20a%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS-Ukraine%20Talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20between%20the%20Ukrainian%20team%2C%20led%20by%20defence%20minister%20Rustem%20Umerov%2C%20and%20the%20Americans%20finished%20late%20Sunday%20night.%20%26quot%3BThe%20discussion%20was%20productive%20and%20focused%20--%20we%20addressed%20key%20points%20including%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20Umerov%20said%20on%20social%20media%2C%20adding%20Ukraine%20was%20working%20to%20make%20its%20goal%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bjust%20and%20lasting%20peace%26quot%3B%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20had%20previously%20said%20proposals%20to%20protect%20energy%20facilities%20and%20critical%20infrastructure%20would%20be%20on%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20evening%20address%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20the%20only%20one%20who%20is%20dragging%20this%20war%20out%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20we%20talk%20about%20with%20our%20partners%2C%20we%20need%20to%20push%20Putin%20to%20give%20a%20real%20order%20to%20stop%20the%20strikes%3A%20the%20one%20who%20brought%20this%20war%20must%20take%20it%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20also%20urged%20his%20country's%20allies%20to%20put%20fresh%20pressure%20on%20Russia.%20%26quot%3BNew%20decisions%20and%20new%20pressure%20on%20Moscow%20are%20needed%20to%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20these%20strikes%20and%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS-Russia%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cb%20data-olk-copy-source%3D%5C%22MailCompose%5C%22%3ENegotiations%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20were%20set%20for%20Monday%2C%20with%20Russian%20state%20media%20reporting%20Moscow's%20delegation%20had%20arrived%20in%20Riyadh%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20this%2C%20American%20envoy%20Steve%20Witkoff%20voiced%20optimism%20that%20any%20agreement%20struck%20would%20pave%20the%20way%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-on%26quot%3B%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20on%20Monday%20some%20real%20progress%2C%20particularly%20as%20it%20affects%20a%20Black%20Sea%20ceasefire%20on%20ships%20between%20both%20countries.%20And%20from%20that%20you'll%20naturally%20gravitate%20to%20a%20full-on%20shooting%20ceasefire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Kremlin%20on%20Sunday%20downplayed%20expectations%20of%20a%20rapid%20resolution%2C%20saying%20talks%20were%20just%20beginning.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20only%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20Kremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20told%20Russian%20state%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20were%20many%20outstanding%20questions%20over%20how%20a%20potential%20ceasefire%20might%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20rejected%20a%20joint%20US-Ukrainian%20call%20for%20a%20full%20and%20immediate%2030-day%20pause%2C%20proposing%20instead%20a%20halt%20in%20attacks%20only%20on%20energy%20facilities.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20difficult%20negotiations%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Peskov%20said%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20published%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20heads%20into%20the%20Saudi%20talks%20after%20a%20rapprochement%20with%20Washington%20under%20Trump%20that%20has%20boosted%20confidence%20in%20the%20Kremlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeskov%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20for%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation%20in%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20spheres%20between%20our%20countries%20cannot%20be%20overstated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20disagree%20on%20some%20things%20but%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20we%20should%20deprive%20ourselves%20of%20mutual%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoscow's%20Black%20Sea%20Agenda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%26quot%3B%20focus%20in%20its%20talks%20with%20the%20US%20would%20be%20a%20possible%20resumption%20of%20a%202022%20Black%20Sea%20grain%20deal%20that%20ensured%20safe%20navigation%20for%20Ukrainian%20farm%20exports%20via%20the%20Black%20Sea.%20%26quot%3BOn%20Monday%2C%20we%20mainly%20intend%20to%20discuss%20President%20Putin's%20agreement%20to%20resume%20the%20so-called%20Black%20Sea%20initiative%2C%20and%20our%20negotiators%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20discuss%20the%20nuances%20around%20this%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Peskov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20deal%20--%20brokered%20by%20Turkey%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20--%20in%202023%2C%20accusing%20the%20West%20of%20failing%20to%20uphold%20its%20commitments%20to%20ease%20sanctions%20on%20Russia's%20own%20exports%20of%20farm%20produce%20and%20fertilisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Ukrainian%20official%20previously%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP%20that%20Kyiv%20would%20propose%20a%20broader%20ceasefire%2C%20covering%20attacks%20on%20energy%20facilities%2C%20infrastructure%20and%20naval%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrone%20Strikes%20Before%20Talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20launched%20fresh%20drone%20attacks%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20negotiations.%20Ukrainian%20officials%20said%20a%20Russian%20drone%20attack%20killed%20three%20civilians%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20including%20a%20five-year-old%20girl%20and%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20air%20force%20said%20Russia%20launched%20147%20drones%20at%20the%20country%20in%20the%20latest%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20meanwhile%20said%20it%20had%20repelled%20nearly%2060%20Ukrainian%20drones%20overnight.%20Officials%20said%20one%20man%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20southern%20Rostov%20region%20of%20Russia%20when%20his%20car%20was%20set%20alight%20by%20falling%20drone%20debris%2C%20and%20a%20woman%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20Belgorod%20border%20region%2C%20also%20by%20a%20drone%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20army%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20it%20had%20captured%20a%20small%20village%20in%20its%20eastern%20Lugansk%20region%2C%20a%20rare%20battlefield%20success%20for%20Kyiv's%20struggling%20forces.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742788080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5hbdstm_us-ukraine-russia_625x300_24_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgulf-in-us-russian-expectations-as-ukraine-peace-deal-talks-begin-in-saudi-7995523%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20and%20Ukrainian%20officials%20met%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20on%20Sunday%20night%20for%20%26quot%3Bproductive%20and%20focused%26quot%3B%20talks%20on%20de-escalating%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%20with%20Washington%20hoping%20for%20%26quot%3Breal%20progress%26quot%3B%20even%20as%20Moscow%20warned%20of%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20negotiations%26quot%3B%20ahead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgulf-in-us-russian-expectations-as-ukraine-peace-deal-talks-begin-in-saudi-7995523%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%2C%20Salman%20on%20Sameer%20Anjaan%20giving%20hit%20songs%20to%20Rishi%