0Jewish%20passengers%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20Mexico%20to%20Texas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20passenger%20says%20a%20pilot%20forced%20him%20out%20of%20the%20airplane%20bathroom%20for%20taking%20too%20long.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20complaint%20accuses%20United%20Airlines%20and%20federal%20agencies%20of%20physical%20harm%20and%20discrimination.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Cspan%3EOrthodox%20Jewish%20%3C%2Fspan%3Epassenger%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Funited-airlines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20flight%20says%20a%20pilot%20forcibly%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20airplane's%20bathroom%20while%20he%20was%20experiencing%20constipation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.638777%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.638777.2.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20this%20week%2C%20Yisroel%20Liebb%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bvisibly%20enraged%26quot%3B%20pilot%20broke%20the%20lock%20on%20the%20restroom%20door%20and%20forced%20Liebb%20out%20while%20his%20pants%20were%20around%20his%20ankles%2C%20exposing%20his%20genitalia%20to%20other%20nearby%20passengers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiebb%20and%20another%20passenger%20he%20was%20traveling%20with%2C%20Jacob%20Sebbag%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Jewish%2C%20claim%20they%20suffered%20physical%20injuries%2C%20emotional%20distress%2C%20and%20discrimination%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20airline%20staff%20and%20federal%20agents%20on%20the%20flight%20from%20Tulum%2C%20Mexico%2C%20to%20Houston%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20events%20unfolded%20on%20January%2028%2C%202025%2C%20after%20a%20flight%20attendant%20woke%20Sebbag%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20check%20on%20Liebb%2C%20who%20had%20been%20in%20the%20bathroom%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiebb%20responded%20that%20he%20