igcaption%3EEmma%20La%20Teace%20said%20her%20Havila%20Voyages%20ferry%20was%20as%20nice%20as%20a%20conventional%20cruise.%3Cp%3EHavila%20Voyages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20La%20Teace%20spent%2012%20days%20cruising%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%20and%20Norway%20with%20Havila%20Voyages%2C%20a%20Norwegian%20ferry%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20ocean%20cruises%2C%20which%20often%20spend%20a%20day%20at%20one%20destination%2C%20the%20ferry%20stopped%20at%20up%20to%20seven%20ports%20daily%2C%20lingering%20between%2020%20minutes%20to%20two%20hours%20at%20each%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20much%20prefer%20to%20have%20lots%20of%20little%20ports%20a%20day%20rather%20than%20one%20really%20long%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20La%20Teace%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20put%20on%20my%20coat%20and%20snow%20boots%2C%20run%20outside%2C%20have%20a%20look%20at%20the%20town%2C%20and%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20onboard%20entertainment%20or%20traditional%20theater.%20Still%2C%20she%20had%20plenty%20of%20fun%2C%20and%20the%20food%20and%20cabin%20were%20surprisingly%20comparable%20to%20those%20of%20a%20conventional%20cruise%20liner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20every%20bit%20as%20nice%20as%20a%20cruise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20people%20would%20like%20that%20if%20they%20did%20cruising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Pro%20tip%3A%20La%20Teace%20said%20if%20you%20like%20Alaska%20voyages%2C%20you'll%20likely%20enjoy%20Norway%2C%20too.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20you%20prefer%20beachy%20Caribbean%20cruises%2C%20you'll%20likely%20appreciate%20Mediterranean%20and%20Canary%20Islands%20itineraries.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Consider%20when%20a%20balcony%20cabin%20(virtual%20or%20not)%20is%20worth%20the%20cost.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emma%20Le%20Teace%20standing%20on%20cruise%20balcony%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddbb67b8b41a9673fb68c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmma%20Le%20Teace%20is%20more%20inclined%20to%20book%20a%20balcony%20cabin%20for%20an%20exciting%20itinerary%20far%20from%20home%20in%20the%20UK.%3Cp%3EEmma%20Le%20Teace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20budget%20cruiser%2C%20Le%20Teace%20frequently%20opts%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-getting-booted-from-overbooked-cruise-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bguaranteed%26quot%3B%20inside%20cabins%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20exciting%20the%20itinerary%2C%20and%20the%20further%20she%20is%20from%20home%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20she%20will%20splurge%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-wonder-vs-icon-of-the-seas-balcony-cabin-compared-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebalcony%20cabin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20going%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Alaska%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20want%20to%20see%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20balcony%26quot%3B%20cabins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20these%20accommodations%20have%20a%20large%20digital%20screen%20that%20displays%20a%20live%20view%20of%20the%20ship's%20exterior%2C%20akin%20to%20a%20real%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20Le%20Teace%20said%20it%20was%20confusing%3A%20The%20screen%20was%20on%20the%20wrong%20wall%20and%20showed%20the%20view%20from%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20helpful%20to%20check%20the%20weather%3F%20Yes.%20Was%20it%20nice%20to%20see%20the%20birds%20flying%20by%3F%20Yes.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20didn't%20convince%20me%20in%20any%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20go%20out%20of%20her%20way%20for